sequenceDiagram
    participant APP as 애플리케이션
    participant SE as WebSocketSession
    participant Q as pendingWrites Queue
    participant SEL as NIO Selector
    participant CH as SocketChannel

    APP->>SE: sendText("메시지")
    SE->>SE: frameEncoder.encodeText()<br/>WebSocket 프레임 생성

    Note over SE,Q: scheduleWrite() 즉시 반환
    SE->>Q: pendingWrites.add(buf)
    SE->>SEL: OP_WRITE 등록 + selector.wakeup()
    SE-->>APP: 반환 완료 (블로킹 없음)

    Note over SEL: OP_WRITE 이벤트 발생
    SEL->>SE: write(SelectionKey)

    loop pendingWrites 소진까지
        SE->>CH: channel.write(buf)
        alt 소켓 버퍼 가득 참 (백프레셔)
            CH-->>SE: 일부만 전송 buf.hasRemaining = true
            SE-->>SEL: 다음 OP_WRITE까지 대기
        else 버퍼 전송 완료
            SE->>Q: pendingWrites.poll()
        end
    end

    Note over SE,SEL: 큐 비워짐
    SE->>SEL: OP_WRITE 관심 해제

    alt isClosePending == true
        SE->>CH: channel.close()
        SE->>SE: OnClose 호출
    end
